<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <h2 id="buffer-list"><i class="icon-th-list"></i> Buffer List</h2>
        <P>
            We open the buffer list window by pressing <kbd>C</kbd>-<kbd>x</kbd> <kbd>C</kbd>-<kbd>b</kbd>
            and once there we can use the following keystrokes:
        </p>
        <table class="table table-striped table-sm">
            <thead class="thead-dark">
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col">Keystroke</th>
                    <th scope="col">Action</th>
                    <th scope="col">Occurs</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>d</kbd></td>
                    <td>Marks buffer for deletion</td>
                    <td>When you press <kbd>x</kbd></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>f</kbd></td>
                    <td>Displayes selected buffer in current window</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>m</kbd></td>
                    <td>Marks buffer to be displayed in another window</td>
                    <td>When you press <kbd>v</kbd></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>n</kbd></td>
                    <td>Moves to the next buffer in the list (i.e., down one line).</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>p</kbd></td>
                    <td>Moves to the previous buffer in the list (i.e., up one line).</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>q</kbd></td>
                    <td>Quits buffer list</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>s</kbd></td>
                    <td>Saves the selected buffer</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>u</kbd></td>
                    <td>Unmarks the selected buffer</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>v</kbd></td>
                    <td>Displayed marked buffers</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>x</kbd></td>
                    <td>Execute commands on marked buffers</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>%</kbd></td>
                    <td>Toggles read-only mode for the selected buffer</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>~</kbd></td>
                    <td>Marks the buffer as modified and do not save changes yet</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>1</kbd></td>
                    <td>Displays buffer in full screen</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><kbd>2</kbd></td>
                    <td>Displays buffer in next horizontal window</td>
                    <td>Immediately</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</div>
